<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-698] Generated module list should contain atoms, not strings</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-698</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The generated list of modules in the .app file should contain atoms, not lists. Please refer to the official Erlang documentation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
